<Body>     	<Title>沙县高砂镇发生森林火灾</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009-02-13</ReportTime>
	<Content>

		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1">据<Participant sid="s1">省森林防火指挥部</Participant><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">消息</Denoter>，</Event><Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">昨日中午</Time>，<Location lid="l2">沙县高砂镇端溪村</Location>发生<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">森林火灾</Denoter></Event>，因风力过大，<Event eid="e3"><Object sid="s3">火灾</Object>迅速<Denoter did="d3" type="movement">蔓延</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter>发生</Event>后，<Event eid="e5">当地在第一时间内<Denoter did="d5" type="operation">组织</Denoter>各种<Object oid="o5" sid="s6">专业力量</Object>全力</Event><Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d6" type="operation">扑救</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e7">鹰厦铁路因火灾受阻的<Object sid="s7">部分列车</Object>于<Time tid="t7" type="relTime">昨晚7时30分</Time>全部恢复<Denoter did="d7" type="stateChange">正常运行</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e8"><Time tid="t8" type="timeInterval">截至今日零时</Time>，<Object oid="o8">火势</Object>已基本得到<Denoter did="d8" type="operation">控制</Denoter></Event>，没有人员伤亡报告。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e9" type="thoughtevent">在<Denoter did="d9" type="perception">获悉</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e10"><Location lid="l10">沙县高砂镇</Location>发生<Denoter did="d10" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter></Event>后，<Event eid="e11" type="thoughtevent" >出差在外的<Participant sid="s11">省委书记卢展工、省长黄小晶</Participant>立即作出重要<Denoter did="d11" type="statement">指示</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e12">要求抓紧做好<Denoter did="d12" type="operation">扑火</Denoter></Event>和<Event eid="e13"><Denoter did="d13" type="operation">防范</Denoter>工作</Event>，<Event eid="e14"><Denoter did="d14" type="statement">确保</Denoter>人民生命财产安全</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e15">国家森林防火指挥部总指挥、国家林业局局长<Participant sid="s15">贾治邦</Participant>对火灾扑救工作<Denoter did="d15" type="action">提出</Denoter>具体<Object oid="o15">要求</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e16">出差在外的省委常委、常务副省长<Participant sid="s16">张昌平</Participant>立即<Denoter did="d16" type="movement">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l16" type="destination">省森林防火指挥部</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e17">与先期坐镇指挥的省委常委、副省长<Participant sid="s17">陈桦</Participant>一同<Denoter did="d17" type="operation">部署</Denoter><Object oid="o17">扑救工作</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e18"><Participant sid="s18">省森林防火指挥部</Participant>迅速把<Object oid="o18">指示精神</Object>向各地<Denoter did="d18" type="statement">传达</Denoter></Event>，贯彻落实。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e19">据<Denoter did="d19" type="statement">介绍</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e20"><Time tid="t20" type="relTime">昨日13时40分许</Time>，<Participant sid="s20">高砂镇防火办</Participant><Denoter did="d20" type="action">接到</Denoter>农民<Object oid="o20">报告</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e21"><Location lid="l21">端溪村</Location>发生<Denoter did="d22" type="emergency">森林火灾</Denoter></Event>，由于风大，<Event eid="e22"><Object sid="s22">火灾</Object><Denoter did="d22" type="movement">蔓延</Denoter>迅速</Event>，<Event eid="e23"><Object sid="s23">火苗</Object><Denoter  did="d23" type="movement">飞过</Denoter><Location lid="l23">沙溪河</Location></Event>，引起<Event eid="e24"><Location lid="l24">对岸</Location><Denoter did="d24" type="action">起火</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e25">并<Denoter did="d25" type="movement">越过</Denoter><Location lid="l25">高速公路</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e26"><Location lid="l26">向不同方向</Location><Denoter did="d26" type="movement">蔓延</Denoter></Event>，形成大连山隧道、高砂镇龙江村、青州镇涌溪村多个火点。</Sentence><Sentence>受火灾影响，当地部分高速公路、铁路和电力一度受到较大影响。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e27"><Denoter did="d27" type="action">接到</Denoter>火灾<Object oid="o27">报告</Object></Event>后，<Event eid="e28"><Participant sid="s28">各级各有关部门</Participant>在第一时间立即<Denoter did="d28" type="operation">行动</Denoter>起来</Event>，<Event eid="e29">省森林防火指挥部和三明市、沙县各级<Participant sid="s29">领导干部</Participant>均在第一时间<Denoter did="d29" type="movement">赶往</Denoter><Location lid="l29" type="destination">火场</Location></Event><Event eid="e30"><Denoter did="d30" type="operation">指挥</Denoter>扑救</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e31"><Participant sid="s31">三明市</Participant>立即<Denoter did="d31" type="operation">成立</Denoter>前线扑火<Participant oid="o31">指挥部</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e32">组织森林、消防、武警官兵和专业扑火队伍以及党政干部<Participant sid="s32">1500多人</Participant>，分五个片区进行<Denoter did="d32" type="operation">扑火</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event polarity="negative" eid="e33"><Time tid="t33" type="timeInterval">截至今日零时</Time>，没有造成人员<Denoter did="d33" type="stateChange">伤亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e34"><Object oid="o34">火烧面积</Object>和<Object oid="o34">起火原因</Object>仍在<Denoter did="d34" type="operation">调查</Denoter>之中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	
